sailpoint.object
Class LiveReport

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      sailpoint.object.LiveReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
public class LiveReport
extends AbstractXmlObject

Configuration object for a 'live' report. LiveReports are our latest report implementation. They allow for previewing of report data before the report is run.

LiveReports always display data in a grid format. They can optionally include a table of summary data, or a chart.
